<h2 id='update-teacher-details'>Update Teacher Details</h2>
<p>This endpoint can be used to update all details of a teacher.</p>

<p>On successful completion teacher details will be included in the JSON response.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>http PUT example.com/api/teachers/:id
</code></pre></div><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code><span class="nx">TODO</span>
</code></pre></div><h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>PUT example.com/api/teachers/2327833979673121796</code></p>
